# Smart Student Task Manager - PRD

## Product Idea
A web application that helps students manage study tasks and organize their time efficiently.

## Problem
Students often struggle to organize assignments, deadlines, and study priorities.

## Solution
This application allows students to create tasks, organize them by priority, and track their progress.

## Key Features
- Add study tasks
- Set task priority
- Track progress
- AI suggestions for task priority

## Target Users
- University students
- School students

## Technologies
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- AI APIs
